Body: Description: One of our admins is getting emails about a reached Transfer limit. I can't find the specific setting in the EP console where I can see this Alert and how to check which files were transfered

What We've Learned Updated: - the customer is receiving Transfer limit reached emails even tho they haven't set up an alert for this
- I informed them since it's enabled directly in the Transfer limit section, this is the intended behaviour and it's sent out to all admins
Next Steps Updated: waiting on closure
